headline: 'You Can Make $100,000 A Year Screwing Around With That,' Dave Ramsey Tells 61-Year-Old Struggling To Survive On 25 Hours A Week
summary: A 61-year-old woman named Jenny called "The Ramsey Show” seeking advice after selling her home in Oregon and ending up with $22,000 in savings. She told personal finance coach Dave Ramsey and co-host George Kamel that she works only 25 hours a week ...
